'''Carolyn Griffiths''' {{post-nominals|country=GBR|FREng}} is a [[railway engineer]].  She was the first Chief Inspector of the UK's [[Rail Accident Investigation Branch]] and a President of the [[Institution of Mechanical Engineers]].<ref name=EC/><ref name=IME/><ref name=RE/><ref name=RG/>

Griffiths was elected [[Fellow of the Royal Academy of Engineering]] (FREng) in 2013.<ref>{{cite web|title=New Fellows 2013|url=http://www.raeng.org.uk/news/news-releases/2013/July/60-new-fellows-elected-to-the-academy-for-2013|accessdate=15 August 2018}}</ref>

